dled a different way,\\\" Djokovic said of the scheduling choice.\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 973, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 934, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9376679100625946e-20, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Musetti lost a five-setter to Djokovic at the French for the second time.\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 1048, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1005, \"end\": 1013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9376679100625946e-20, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6115780892429111, \"rank\": 0.5278388536632936, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He squandered a two-set lead in 2021.\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1086, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic, who has not made a tournament final in 2024, next gets 23rd seed Francisco Cerundolo of Argentina in the round of 16 on Monday.\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1173, \"end\": 1182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cerundolo\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cerundolo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cerundolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cerundolo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In that match, he will bid to break his tie with Roger Federer for the career record of 369 Grand